reviewText: um, kendall moore- you wrote the worst review i've ever seen.  are ya kidding me?  less talk about your pig out sessions on the couch and more info about the dvd next time.

I LOVE THE MOVIE! ESPECIALLY LUKE. HE IS SUCH AN ATTRACTIVE MAN. I AM VEERING OFF SUBJECT NOW. THE OC SO SO SUPER AMAZING. I SPEND MOST OF MY DAY SITTING ON MY FUTON WATCHING THE OC WITH DIET SLICE AND A GALLON OF BEN AND JERRY'S. ENJOY THE DVD.. I KNOW I DID.
